patthana23.32:1.1_0: Nahīnaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā majjhimo kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.32:2.1_0: Nahīnaṁ naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā hīno akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.32:3.1_0: Nahīnaṁ naabyākataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca majjhimo abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha,
